      <div class="msgContentFrame">just curious where everyone has been placing their stats.  <br /> <br />I'm currently rank 24 Lnc 27phys  <br />When I first started out I was trying to go for a more rounded balance overall. I would place 1 point each in mnd pie and int every 3 levels then place the rest in Str Vit and Dex. mainly focusing on dex.  <br /> <br />Then after a while I took back all the points I placed in mnd pie and Int and pumped up my Vit  surpassing Dex by a few points but leaving Str my lowest of the &quot;melee&quot; stats.  <br /> <br />Now I'm wondering as post rank 20 more and more game play is going party route (thank you SE i hate solo games) Should I take back the points I put into Vit and redistribute them in STR.  <br /> <br />Current melee stats: <br />STR: 55 (61) <br />Vit: 66 (66) <br />Dex: 58 (61) <br /> <br />I noticed I was doing some pretty poor Dmg vs Rank 30 Leve mobs tonight 30's-40 per hit (3 star mobs) I feel I should be hitting for at least double that. (rank 24 lnc 27 phys)  <br />Maybe once I upgrade to the Iron spear I'll see better #'s.  <div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div>FFXIV has it's first official RMT'r: Zyuu</div></div>
