      <div class="msgContentFrame">I'm currently sitting at Base 32 / 24 LNC, and I've toyed around with my stats quite a few times. Originally I thought high dex was the solution to the high miss rate, but recently I've pumped vit to the cap for my level (88) and done the same with strength, and dex is just staying at it's base value. Honestly I haven't even noticed going from 85 dex back to 17, I still hit often enough to generate tp, and even if I do miss more, that's just more opportunities to feint. I'd say I hit around 65-70% of the time on Light Thrusts still.</div>
