      <div class="msgContentFrame">I know several times in the past this has been talked about, but as Echz said above, the effect of dexterity does not seem to be as great as people say. It seems to be much more weapon- /accessory-based. <br /> <br />I'm a r23 Lancer right now. You can click on the link in my signature to look at my stats. My STR and VIT are sitting right around the &quot;cap&quot; for me, so I've been using my excess points for INT (since I'm an alchemist crafter, I found out having more INT apparently helps my crafting). I've been keeping my DEX down at its base 17, but only recently added more points into it because my friends in my LS have been arguing that the reason I complain about missing so much is because of my low DEX. I disagree though. I think at my current level my biggest problem comes from still using a Bronze Spear against enemies that are yellow or red to me. More often than not, battles are either me hitting 80%+ of the time or hardly at all (in which case, like Echz said, lots of Feinting occurs, and with Invigorate, the occasional hit I DO pull off gives me enough TP to do that). <br /> <br />I think I'm going to redistribute those extra DEX points just back into INT or maybe MND (there's some speculation MND is effective for Lancers, but I don't recall if any research has been done on it. I'll let you know if I notice anything). But this will be primarily for my Alchemy. <br /> <br />As a side note: I understand that Lancers are really meant to be hit a lot, thus a high vitality isn't SUPPOSED to be necessary (I like it mostly because I do a fair amount of soloing, or pulling hate if an enemy starts attacking our healer). In an ideal case, you could probably just focus on pumping up STR and do something crazy with casting abilites, pump some INT and MND. Make yourself a melee/casting support? I don't know. <br /> <br />Edit real fast with my actual stats: <br />Strength:	85 <br />Vitality:	83 <br />Dexterity:	23 <br />Intelligence:	60 <br />Mind:	        14 <br />Piety:	        15 <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Oct 31st 2010  5:44am by ArkWeldwin </span></i><div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div>FFXIV: Laurana Drakoid | Lancer | Alchemist | Rabanastre <br /><a href="http://lodestone.finalfantasyxiv.com/rc/character/status?cicuid=4245640" title="http://lodestone.finalfantasyxiv.com/rc/character/status?cicuid=4245640" rel="external nofollow">http://lodestone.finalfantasyxiv.com/rc/character/status?cicuid=4245640</a></div></div>
